The researcher explained, who would exist direct utility for the investigation participants in a comprehensive investigation of the children, with which assessed would become, whether these showed a degree of overweight-ness or obesity.
It would refer even the occurrence of dark skin folds in the nape and at the interior arm (Akanthosis), that to the probability of metabolism interferences and diabetes in the before stage, examines.
All information confidentially would be treated and would be announced the parents in writing by the physicians. The physicians explain all fair results to the parents and strike them changes of the lifestyle before, that are appropriate to the prevention of diseases.
